{"TopicId":41646,"ForumId":32,"TopicTitle":"Posting screenshots","CreatedByName":"Rassa Farlander","CreatedById":63627,"CreatedDateTime":"2013-08-08T18:59:20Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Rassa Farlander","CreatedById":63627,"CreatedDateTime":"2013-08-08T18:59:20Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003ESo Ive been playing KSP since last December and Ive never posted a screenshot. So the questions are:\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E1. How do I post a screenshot?\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E2. What website is recommended for hosting the images?\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E3. Anything else I should know?\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003ESorry about the rookie question, I feel like such a newb \u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E lol\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EThanks\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"swiftgates24","CreatedById":22280,"CreatedDateTime":"2013-08-08T19:03:01Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E1. Go to Imgur.com (Best image hosting site).\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E2. Click on the Computer on the right.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E3. Find where you screenshot is (KSP screenshot folder by default).\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E4. Select it and upload it.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E5. Once it is done, you should see links for the image on the right. Find the BBCode version (Not Linked BBCode), then copy it.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E6. Paste it here! \u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Rassa Farlander","CreatedById":63627,"CreatedDateTime":"2013-08-08T19:04:17Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EAwesome \u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E Ok one more, what about using the spoilers thing? Whats that all about \u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_tongue.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:P\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"KAO","CreatedById":30795,"CreatedDateTime":"2013-08-08T19:05:24Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003Espoilers are broken\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Rassa Farlander","CreatedById":63627,"CreatedDateTime":"2013-08-08T19:08:51Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EOk sounds simple enough then \u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E Im suprised I havent done this sooner, thanks for the help \u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}